subject: Attention,
body:
Attention,
This is FBI Agent Kennedy Albano, I want to use this opportunity to
inform you that we have arrested the diplomatic agent that refused to
deliver your package worth a sum of $4.5Million USD. Meanwhile, 
we
urge you to respond to this email if you're interested in receiving
your fund with this below information..
Your Name:
Home Address:
Cell Phone:
Occupation:
your Nearest Airport:
Age:
Am looking forward to your immediate response.
Email via (
agentkennedyalbano111@gmail.com
)
Regards.
FBI Agent Kennedy Albano.

subject: Re: Attention,
body:
Hello Agent Kennedy Albano,

Wow, that's quite a surprise! I wasn't aware there was a diplomatic agent with my package. Can you tell me more about this situation? How did you come across this information and what does the package contain?

Looking forward to your response.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Cory
